    <span class="s2" style="font-kerning: none;">The Allied Health Professions Council&nbsp;in its determination to offer efficient to its Clients&nbsp;has introduced a more user-friendly and convenient&nbsp;<b>e-payment</b>&nbsp;system for all its activities and programmes. The new e-payment method has come to replace the traditional<span
