    <span class="s2" style="font-kerning: none;">Accordingly, all Clients are hereby informed that the Council <b>will
            only accept the
            e-payment</b>&nbsp;for its services and it should be&nbsp;noted&nbsp;as such.&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></p><p
